a description</a>.</span></div> <div class="lh-audit__stackpacks"></div> </details> </div><div class="lh-audit lh-audit--binary lh-audit--pass" id="http-status-code"> <details class="lh-expandable-details"> <summary> <div class="lh-audit__header lh-expandable-details__summary"> <span class="lh-audit__score-icon"></span> <span class="lh-audit__title-and-text"> <span class="lh-audit__title"><span>Page has successful HTTP status code</span></span> <span class="lh-audit__display-text"></span> </span> <div class="lh-chevron-container"><svg class="lh-chevron" viewBox="0 0 100 100"> <g class="lh-chevron__lines"> <path class="lh-chevron__line lh-chevron__line-left" d="M10 50h40"></path> <path class="lh-chevron__line lh-chevron__line-right" d="M90 50H50"></path> </g> </svg></div> </div> </summary> <div class="lh-audit__description"><span>Pages with unsuccessful HTTP status codes may not be indexed properly. <a rel="noopener" target="_blank" href="https://developer.chrome.com/docs/lighthouse/seo/http-status-code/?utm_source=lighthouse&amp;utm_medium=lr">Learn more about HTTP status codes</a>.</span></div> <div class="lh-audit__stackpacks"></div> </details> </div><div class="lh-audit lh-audit--binary lh-audit--pass" id="link-text"> <details class="lh-expandable-details"> <summary> <div class="lh-audit__header lh-expandable-details__summary"> <span class="lh-audit__score-icon"></span> <span class="lh-audit__title-and-text"> <span class="lh-audit__title"><span>Links have descriptive text</span></span> <span class="lh-audit__display-text"></span> </span> <div class="lh-chevron-container"><svg class="lh-chevron" viewBox="0 0 100 100"> <g class="lh-chevron__lines"> <path class="lh-chevron__line lh-chevron__line-left" d="M10 50h40"></path> <path class="lh-chevron__line lh-chevron__line-right" d="M90 50H50"></path> </g> </svg></div> </div> </summary> <div class="lh-audit__description"><span>Descriptive link text helps search engines understand your content. <a rel="noopener" target="